M|references|- [ ] 10-Year Target set
M|references|- [ ] mkt str defined (all four parts)
M|references|- [ ] Vision page of V/TO complete
M|references|VB2 focuses on the Traction side of the V/TO: the near-term execution plan.
M|references|| Time | Activity | Details |
M|references||------|----------|---------|
M|references|| 8:00-8:30 | **Check-In** | rv VB1 decisions. Any adjustments needed? Level 10 meeting feedback. |
M|references|| 8:30-10:00 | **3-Year Picture** | Paint a vivid, specific picture of the company in three years. Revenue, profit, headcount, key metrics, qualitative description. |
M|references|| 10:00-10:15 | Break | |
M|references|| 10:15-12:00 | **1-Year Plan** | Set revenue, profit, and 3-7 specific goals for the next twelve months. |
M|references|| 12:00-1:00 | Lunch | |
M|references|| 1:00-2:30 | **Quarterly Rocks** | rv and refine rocks set on Focus Day (or set new ones if Q1 has ended). Apply SMART criteria. |
M|references|| 2:30-2:45 | Break | |
M|references|| 2:45-4:00 | **Issues List** | Build the long-term and short-term Issues Lists. IDS the top 3 strategic issues. |
M|references|| 4:00-4:30 | **V/TO rv** | rv the complete V/TO (both pages). Confirm leadership alignment. |
M|references|| 4:30-5:00 | **Next Steps** | Plan the company-wide V/TO rollout. Schedule the next quarterly ses. |
