M|references|After the initial foundation-building sessions, quarterly sessions follow a consistent format:
M|references|| Time | Activity | Details |
M|references||------|----------|---------|
M|references|| 8:00-8:30 | **Check-In** | Segue, what's working, what's not |
M|references|| 8:30-9:30 | **Previous Quarter Rock rv** | Score each rock (done/not done). Calculate completion rate. Celebrate wins. |
M|references|| 9:30-10:00 | **People Headlines** | rv Accountability Chart. Any people issues? People Analyzer updates. |
M|references|| 10:00-10:15 | Break | |
M|references|| 10:15-11:15 | **V/TO rv** | Quick rv of V/TO for any needed updates. Are we on track for 1-Year Plan? |
M|references|| 11:15-12:00 | **IDS Strategic Issues (Part 1)** | Tackle long-term Issues List items |
M|references|| 12:00-1:00 | Lunch | |
M|references|| 1:00-2:30 | **IDS Strategic Issues (Part 2)** | Continue solving strategic issues |
M|references|| 2:30-2:45 | Break | |
M|references|| 2:45-4:00 | **Set Next Quarter Rocks** | Brainstorm, prioritize, apply SMART, assign owners |
M|references|| 4:00-4:30 | **Cascading Messages and Next Steps** | What messages go to the rest of the company? |
M|references|| 4:30-5:00 | **Conclude** | Rate the ses. Feedback. Confirm next quarterly date. |
